Argentina 1936

Asociación del Fútbol Argentino - Copa Campeonato - 1936.

The season 1936 was divided in 3 cups:
1. Copa de Honor Municipalidad de Buenos Aires.
2. Copa Campeonato.
3. Copa de Oro (between the winners of cups Honor and Campeonato).

The cup Campeonato was the tradional trophy gave to the champion of the league.
Then, the following points are discussed:
River Plate is the champion 1936 because:
a. It won the Copa Campeonato.
b. It won the Copa de Oro.

