River Plate won the Copa Campeonato in this round with the following line-ups:
River Plate: Sirni; Vassini, Fatecchi; Malazzo, Minella, Wergifker;
             Peucelle, Cesarini, Rongo, Moreno, Pedernera.
Quilmes:     Bottaso; Pronato, Rodríguez; Ruggero, Díaz, Martín;
             Neira, Arrillaga, Fernández, Miranda, López.
Ref.: Forte. Field: River Plate. Att.: 7500.

